Bagisto is an open-source eCommerce platform built on Laravel, one of the most popular PHP frameworks. It provides a flexible and modular solution for building online stores, offering features such as:

- Multi-vendor support
- Multi-channel inventory management
- Product management
- Order management
- Customer management
- Various payment gateway integrations

It is particularly suited for developers who want to build custom eCommerce solutions and extend functionality using Laravel's structure. Bagisto is designed to be scalable and customizable, making it a good fit for small businesses as well as large enterprises.
